## ⚠️ Troubleshooting

### ❌ init-sysctl Crash

Fix:

```
initSysctl:
  enabled: false
```

---

### ❌ Helm Validation Error

```
monitoringPasscode required
```

Fix:

```
monitoringPasscode: "admin123"
```

---

### ❌ Edition Error

Fix:

```
community:
  enabled: true
```

---

### ❌ Pod Pending (PVC Issue)

Fix:

```
persistence:
  enabled: false
```

